HEADWORD: Tycoon
<hw>Ty*coon"</hw> <pr>(t⟦isl⟧`k⟦oomac⟧n")</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[Chinese <ets>tai-kun</ets> great prince.]</ety> <def>The title by
